Swiss public transport API

Swiss public transport API

tapi(endpoint, ..., .protocol = "https", .url = "transport.opendata.ch",
  .version = "v1")

Arguments

endpoint

path to api endpoint - there are three endpoints available: locations, connections, and stationboard.
...

named parameters will be translated into a request query
.protocol

protocol to be used
.url

base url
.version

api version

Value

list of dataframes
